node.text:
You reap what you sow 🌱🖤

A simple phrase that has stood the test of time because of its powerful meaning… that is, your future is shaped by your actions today. 

In a world that is full of uncertainty and chaos, be deliberate and firm in your actions. Be aware of who and what you are investing your time and energy in… and always be working towards your goals. 

And yes… my shirt still has paint on it. I am aware. 🤓🖤🤘🏼

All sun. No sand. ⛱🧘🏻‍♀️ Mental rest day to prepare for a crazy busy week. 

Ever have those days where nothing seems to go right? That was me yesterday… but I am ever grateful for my support system that helped reel me back to happiness today. Life is good and will only get better 🖤🤓🤘🏼

#sundayvibes #poolside #happiness #hardwork #tattooedgirls #fitmomlife #freedom #faith #mentalhealth #homesweethome

node.text:
You will face difficulties, not because you are doing something wrong… but because you are doing them right. Face  them with a smile on your face. Because storms are temporary while complacency is a never-ending disease. It will eat away at your soul if you allow it. 
So get up, face the day and be proud of yourself for moving towards your goals, your destiny one day at a time. 

PS. I’m a seatbelt tucker from wayback. Don’t @ me 🤫🤓

#wednesdaywisdom #happiness #hardwork #ridethestorm #faith #freedom #tattooedgirls #fitmomlife #carrides #realestatebroker #bragg #home
